    "#### adding the ohca cases with geometry points to sql \n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "ogr2ogr -f PostgreSQL \\\n",
    "  PG:\"dbname=landuse user=yitong\" \\\n",
    "  3_OHCA_with_geometric_pts.gpkg \\\n",
    "  -nln ohca_cases \\\n",
    "  -lco GEOMETRY_NAME=geom \\\n",
    "  -lco FID=id \\\n",
    "  -nlt PROMOTE_TO_MULTI \\\n",
    "  3_OHCA_with_geometric_pts\n",
    "```"
